node.text: Though her career began in classical music, painting, and analog photography, @HelenaGarza_'s field of inspiration is boundless. In this project, she shares a VR painting – a proposal of reality understood from figurative memories and the present environment in constant change and reconstruction. Learn more about her unique explorations in art at vans.com/offthewall

node.text: In late 2019, just before Covid-19 shut down live performances worldwide, we invited the crowd at @HouseOfVans London to get creative and help make a music video for @JPEGMAFIA. Watch the final edit and get to know the experimental rap artist at vans.com/offthewall

node.text: This week in the shoebox, we're joined by Norwegian singer-songwriter Marie Ulven, better known as @girlinred. Watch art by @AranQuinn come to life as you isten to "We Fell In Love In October" and "Bad Idea."

node.text: We recently asked you guys to send us your most creative clips to help us make the longest manual and you delivered. Thanks to everyone who submitted!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by vans on August 13, 2021 tagging @jjjjound, and @vansvault. May be an image of 1 person and footwear.

node.text: @VansVault and @JJJJound come together to reinterpret the Style 37. The short-lived style was only in production for one year before its design evolved into the Sk8-Hi. Sometime in the 1990s, Vans reissued the Vault by Vans Style 37, and since then, it has been rediscovered as the Sk8-Mid VLT LX. The Vault by Vans x JJJJound Sk8-Mid VLT LX is available tomorrow 8/14 at select Vault dealers globally. For more info, visit vans.com/droplist

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by vans on August 12, 2021. May be an image of footwear.

node.text: With the Eco Theory collection, we set out to rebuild more thoughtful versions of our Classics with environmental consciousness in mind. Learn more about the responsibly sourced materials we used on the Old Skool Decon, Skate Sk8-Hi Tapered, and Authentic and shop the collection at vans.com/news
